TEXT_68=But thousands of people with the flu develop pneumonia or a brain infection. They need to stay in the hospital. About 36,000 people in the U.S.\u00A0die each year of problems from the flu.
TEXT_67=Millions of people in the United States get the flu each year. Most get better within a week or two.
