TEXT_47=The flu can make asthma, breathing problems, and other long-term illnesses worse.
TEXT_46=Some people may not feel like eating.
TEXT_45=Most symptoms go away in 4-7 days. The cough and tired feeling may last for weeks. Sometimes, the fever comes back.
